        Makes a build history-file that is routable via the API
        Parameters:
        status - the success status of the build
        buildID - id of the build, for example a commit-id
        contributor - who is the owner of the latest commit
        timestamp - the time of the CI-build
        output - any other information to be recorded
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - if the template is missing or file cannot be saved
